<div class="listings">
<h2>Top Menu</h2>
<ul>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:write) %> ... add new entry</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:search) %> ... search entries</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:settings) %> ... change session settings</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:logout) %> ... logout and discard settings</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:help) %> ... show this help</li>
</ul>

<h2>Page Cursor</h2>
<ul>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:previous) %> ... go previous page</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:next) %> ... go next page</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:top) %> ... go top of this page</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:bottom) %> ... go bottom of this page</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:more) %> ... go detailed page which shows omitted entries/comments of a list</li>
</ul>

<h2>Page Menu</h2>
<ul>
  <li>[inbox] ... show your entries in 'home' excluding archived entries</li>
  <li>[all] ... show all of your entries in 'home' including archived entries</li>
  <li>[me] ... show your profile</li>
  <li>[groups] ... show entries of groups you are joining</li>
  <li>[pin] ... show pinned entries</li>
  <li><%= service_icon_tag('http://friendfeed.com/static/images/icons/internal.png', 'FriendFeed', 'FriendFeed') %> ... show filtered entries by specified service</li>
  <li>(user name) ... show user profile</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:url) %> ... show seach result page of entries which relates to specified link</li>
</ul>

<h2>Entry Edit Operation</h2>

<ul>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:comment_add, 'comment') %> ... add comment to the entry</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:like) %> ... add 'like'</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:star) %> ... show who 'like'd it; delete your 'like' once you 'like'd it</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:reshare) %> ... reshare the entry (make new entry based on the entry)</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:comment_edit) %> ... edit the comment</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:delete) %> ... delete the entry/comment</li>
</ul>

<h2>Pin Operation</h2>

<ul>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:pin) %> ... add pin to the entry; pinned entries keep on showing in [inbox] and [pin]</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:pinned) %> ... unpin the entry and archive it to [all]</li>
  <li><%= submit_tag('mark as read') %> ... archive all entries in [inbox] to [all] except pinned entries</li>
</ul>

<h2>User Filter</h2>

<p>These filters are shown at the top of user profile page.</p>

<ul>
  <li>[self] ... show entries of the user</li>
  <li>[friends] ... show entries of the user + his/her friends</li>
  <li>[likes] ... show entries the user 'like'd</li>
  <li>[comments] ... show entries the user commented</li>
  <li>[liked] ... show entries of the user which is commented by other</li>
  <li>[commented] ... show entries of the user which is commented or 'like'd</li>
</ul>

<h2>Others</h2>
<ul>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:private) %> ... the entry is private</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:group) %> ... the entry is for a group</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:go) %> ... link to go source site</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:comment) %> ... self comment by the entry author</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:friend_comment) %> ... comment from friends of the entry author</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:related) %> ... showing related entries</li>
</ul>
</div>

